Bangladesh  Sugar & Food Industries
Corp., a state-owned producer, is seeking to buy 50,000 metric
tons of white, or refined sugar, according to Ferdous Begum,
secretary of the company.  The deadline for 25,000 metric tons is 11 a.m. Dhaka,
Bangladesh, time on March 10, according to a notice on the
companyâ€™s website. The deadline for the other 25,000 tons is 11
